## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing
- Test at 390×844 (iPhone), 768×1024 (iPad), and 1440px (desktop)
- Verify all interactive elements have ≥48px touch targets on mobile
- Ensure board scrolls smoothly and doesn't break layout
- Check that collapsible panels work and persist state

> [!IMPORTANT]
> These are purely CSS/UX changes — no game logic is modified. The server.js file is untouched.
